snippet.title: Clock Out at 2: Survive the Workplace
snippet.description:
Maintain your mental health or face being sent to HR.

👉 Want to see the kind of coworker you work with? If so, click here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dSs9njA3WaA&list=PLIsNoAUpSq32WMGhWmqeFNZhGapQekuux

Celia, an Afro-Latina woman, who is trying to survive another day at work. You need to clock out early but the company culture won't allow it.

To make matters worse, ever since the “incident” and you’ve been seeing strange and terrifying creatures.

Is It Real? Or Is the Stress Getting to You?

Make it to the end of the day while balancing your mental health or face being sent to HR.

A 2D Roguelite Visual Novel set in the modern horror known as the "workplace."
Features over 50,000 words of non-repetitive text and multiple endings.
Full voice-over lines with a professional cast.
There are monsters lurking everywhere, including the workplace. There might be one lurking - Inside of you. Can you "Clock Out at 2"?🕑

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3235690/Clock_Out_at_2/
